metadata.name: Blissfully Stressed
metadata.description: In a fit of frustration with myself, I wrote a slew of self-defeating things on this page. The next day, I decided this wasn't a healthy way to treat yourself & began attempting to cover them up with something beautiful instead.
metadata.Feelings: of overcoming self doubt, hatred, and discontent.

attributes.value: Watercolor, Acrylic Paint Pens, Ink, and a "PAID" sticker from my local grocery store
